View.Name: activitystudentitem_view
View.SQLQuery: SELECT DISTINCT st.refid, st.session_refid AS sessionid, st."time", item.item_reference AS itemreference, st.max_score AS maxscore, st.user_flagged AS userflagged, item.organisation_id AS organisationid, item.item_pool_id AS itempoolid, item.type FROM (student_item st JOIN item item ON (((st.item_reference)::text = (item.item_reference)::text)));

View.Name: activitystudentquestion_view
View.SQLQuery: SELECT DISTINCT sq.refid, sq.question_reference AS questionreference, sq.student_item_refid AS studentitemrefid, sq.actual_response AS actualresponse, question.rubric_reference AS rubricreference, question.question_type AS questiontype FROM (student_question sq JOIN question question ON (((sq.question_reference)::text = (question.question_reference)::text)));

View.Name: activitystudentscore_view
View.SQLQuery: SELECT DISTINCT ss.response_id AS responseid, ss.score_reference AS scorereference, ss.staff_personal_refid AS staffpersonalrefid, ss.student_question_refid AS studentquestionrefid, ss.attemted AS attempted, ss.value, ss.weight, ss.max_score AS maxscore, ss.score, score.title, score.description, score.automarkable, score.correct_response AS correctresponse FROM (student_score ss JOIN score score ON (((ss.score_reference)::text = (score.score_reference)::text)));
